reviewText: The narrator sounded like he was doing an oral report about Billy Gohl to his class of teenagers .  He kept repeating Billy Gohl's name throughout. Well, I guess he wanted to make sure we knew who he was talking about. Oh, how I wish I'd have paid attention to the one-star reviews.  It was a huge waste, and it wasn't even interesting.
Title: America's Worst Serial Killer Ever The Story of Billy Gohl
